@dwmkerr mentioned in #111 that it would be nice to make a video to highlight the dev process.

In addition, I think it would be great to create a gif for the `README.md` that shows Oscar in action on the CLI or Slack. Perhaps we could ask him about trending repositories, open pull requests and/or jokes?

Probably best to do this closer to the submission date to avoid having to re-shoot it on every merge.

